00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:23,119
But this only eases things for now.

594
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:25,000
It can't solve the root problem.

595
00:29:25,519 --> 00:29:26,039
That's true.

596
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,720
I've already contacted Li Guangtian.

597
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:29,359
He's helping me with technical support.

598
00:29:29,799 --> 00:29:31,880
We're upgrading the ordering app.

599
00:29:32,039 --> 00:29:32,720
Problems

600
00:29:32,759 --> 00:29:33,480
