607
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:44,720
I haven't come with anyone.

608
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:46,720
Right.

609
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,039
I, uh...

610
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:48,720
No, not...

611
00:29:48,759 --> 00:29:49,839
It's my first time here.

612
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,759
First time at this place.

