623
00:30:27,799 --> 00:30:29,960
Our restaurant shows up in nearby eats.

624
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,720
That's awesome!

625
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:32,279
Exactly.

626
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,960
So just scan it

627
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:35,680
