629
00:30:37,519 --> 00:30:37,920
Right.

630
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,200
That's really impressive.

631
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:42,519
Mainly because Mingliang did the prep work well.

632
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,440
My job

633
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,720
