636
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:47,759
Yeah.

637
00:30:47,759 --> 00:30:48,640
They've got skills.

638
00:30:49,359 --> 00:30:50,960
So you don't dislike him now?

639
00:30:51,519 --> 00:30:52,920
Who said I did?

640
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:54,200
You brat.

641
00:30:56,359 --> 00:30:56,920
Aunt Bayar.

642
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:57,920
You try scanning it too.

643
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:58,359
Okay.

644
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,039
I'll give it a try.

645
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:01,119
Do you know how to scan?

646
00:31:01,359 --> 00:31:02,440
