650
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,279
Here.

651
00:31:10,359 --> 00:31:11,279
A treat for you.

652
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,039
Sea intestine rice bowl.

653
00:31:15,319 --> 00:31:16,000
