655
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,400
Our Yueyue

656
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,920
went to great lengths so you could eat this hometown dish.

657
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,759
She worked super hard for it.

658
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,279
I washed the sea intestines.

659
00:31:28,279 --> 00:31:29,200
I fried the rice.

660
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,400
I mixed the chives and seasoning.

661
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,240
Yueyue, what did you do?

662
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,480
She just plated it.

663
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,079
You go first.

664
00:31:46,759 --> 00:31:48,200
Is Mama A'isha doing well?

665
00:31:48,799 --> 00:31:49,440
She's alright.

666
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,680
She just likes to act tough.

667
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:53,759
Doesn't want us to worry.

668
00:31:56,599 --> 00:31:59,039
I'm heading to Bulgan Reserve in a couple days.

669
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,000
When I get back,

670
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:00,960
I'll go see her.

671
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:02,799
Bulgan.

672
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:05,680
How many days?

673
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,920
Hard to say.

674
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:09,640
What's wrong?

675
00:32:10,799 --> 00:32:11,279
It's nothing.

676
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:14,039
Isn't Mom's birthday in a few days?

677
00:32:17,599 --> 00:32:19,160
I'll adjust my schedule then.

678
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:19,720
It's fine.

679
00:32:19,799 --> 00:32:20,480
You do your thing.

680
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,559
It's just a birthday.

681
00:32:21,839 --> 00:32:22,799
We'll skip it this year.

682
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,200
There's always next year.

683
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,119
And the year after.

684
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,960
And many more years to come.

685
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:33,279
Right.

686
00:32:34,039 --> 00:32:34,920
Many more years.

687
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:36,960
We celebrate every year.

688
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:48,880
Okay.

689
00:32:49,480 --> 00:32:49,960
Thank you.

690
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:54,160
My name is Lu Wenchang.

691
00:32:54,759 --> 00:32:55,920
I'm also in the restaurant business.

692
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,759
My place is over on Yashan North Road.

693
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:00,400
Hello, Boss Lu.

694
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:00,960
Ming Liang.

695
00:33:01,519 --> 00:33:02,440
You came here today—

696
00:33:02,599 --> 00:33:03,480
Is there something I can help with?

697
00:33:04,839 --> 00:33:05,720
I'll get straight to the point.

698
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:06,079
Alright.

699
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,279
I want to join your restaurant as a partner.

700
00:33:10,319 --> 00:33:12,200
