701
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:15,160
This year, I've been thinking about expanding.

702
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,880
I've considered many ways.

703
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:17,960
None of them really worked.

704
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,319
I know about your place too.

705
00:33:19,519 --> 00:33:22,440
You just turned things around these past months.

706
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:23,440
Yes, that's right.

707
00:33:23,759 --> 00:33:25,000
So, my friend—

708
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:26,400
I'll invest the money.

709
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,440
You bring the reputation.

710
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:30,680
Let's make the Hong Shiliu brand

711
00:33:31,079 --> 00:33:31,960
bigger and stronger.

712
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:33,599
Don't worry.

713
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,640
I can pay extra for the partnership fee.

714
00:33:36,039 --> 00:33:37,759
I promise I won't ruin your reputation.

715
00:33:39,279 --> 00:33:41,039
Boss Lu, just like you said—

716
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:42,400
Our Hong Shiliu restaurant

717
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,880
only turned things around recently.

718
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,279
So personally, I think

719
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,400
our foundation isn't solid yet.

720
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:51,359
We're not ready to open franchise stores.

721
00:33:51,839 --> 00:33:52,440
If I were to

722
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,160
just chase short-term gains,

723
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,400
and agreed to you today,

724
00:33:55,559 --> 00:33:57,680
I might let you down.

725
00:33:57,799 --> 00:34:00,079
And your money could go to waste.

726
00:34:01,039 --> 00:34:02,000
So, Boss Lu—

727
00:34:02,519 --> 00:34:03,480
About the partnership,

728
00:34:04,599 --> 00:34:05,680
I can't agree to it.

729
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:08,199
Then I was a bit abrupt today.

730
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:09,920
Sorry about that.

731
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,239
I'll let you get back to work.

732
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:12,239
I'm heading out.

733
00:34:14,039 --> 00:34:14,559
Boss Lu—

734
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:16,760
I can

735
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,360
share with you

736
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,679
what I've learned these past months.

737
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:21,000
Maybe

738
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:22,960
it could help you.

739
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,480
Sure.

740
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:37,280
So you're really not considering the partnership?

741
00:34:39,639 --> 00:34:40,960
I thought it over before refusing.

742
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,400
Our restaurant suddenly got popular.

743
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,599
It's already shown our weaknesses.

744
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:48,280
We've known each other for a while now.

745
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,360
You know what kind of person I am.

746
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,599
I'm someone who prefers stability.

747
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:54,719
I like steady progress.

748
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,119
But I really think this is an opportunity.

749
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,960
If you turn it down now,

750
00:35:00,119 --> 00:35:01,920
it'll be hard to rely on brand power

751
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:03,199
to open chain stores in the future.

752
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,800
It'll be tough.

753
00:35:05,719 --> 00:35:06,960
I never planned on going chain.

754
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:09,920
Dong Ge—

755
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:13,440
When I first took over the restaurant,

756
00:35:13,719 --> 00:35:15,400
it was to keep this family together.

757
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:17,639
Now,

758
00:35:18,239 --> 00:35:19,440
what worries me most

759
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,440
is my mom's health.

760
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,880
Business is important,

761
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,639
but I don't want to lose sight of what matters.

762
00:35:38,119 --> 00:35:38,679
My mom,

763
00:35:39,199 --> 00:35:40,000
Mama Bayar,

764
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:40,880
Murat's Dad—

765
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:43,159
I'm sure they all feel the same.

766
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,519
When it comes to management,

767
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:46,639
you're the real expert.

768
00:35:47,159 --> 00:35:48,719
Once things settle down here,

769
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,000
it'll need someone like you

770
00:35:51,239 --> 00:35:52,599
to run it professionally.

771
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:55,039
I'll just take my mom out to have fun.

772
00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:56,440
Go wherever she wants.

773
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:57,960
Be with her every day.

774
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,239
Make sure she's happy every day.

775
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,199
What about your own life?

776
00:36:14,239 --> 00:36:15,960
This is the life I want most right now.

777
00:36:20,159 --> 00:36:21,639
Didn't expect someone your age

778
00:36:21,639 --> 00:36:23,119
to see things so clearly.

779
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,239
Let me tell you

780
00:36:28,239 --> 00:36:29,719
the story of me and my ex-wife.

781
00:36:37,719 --> 00:36:38,639
I'm all ears.

782
00:36:45,119 --> 00:36:45,800
The two of us,

783
00:36:48,039 --> 00:36:49,519
from dating to marriage,

784
00:36:51,119 --> 00:36:52,079
for so many years.

785
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,519
I was poor all those years.

786
00:36:58,400 --> 00:36:59,199
Had nothing.

787
00:37:00,559 --> 00:37:01,559
I remember one time—

788
00:37:02,159 --> 00:37:03,159
We owed rent.

789
00:37:03,719 --> 00:37:05,599
The landlord kicked us out in the middle of the night.

790
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:10,719
We didn't want to spend money on a hotel.

791
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,639
So we dragged our luggage

792
00:37:15,039 --> 00:37:16,400
and stayed under a bridge.

793
00:37:18,639 --> 00:37:19,320
Just toughed it out.

794
00:37:21,239 --> 00:37:22,519
She never complained.

795
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:26,039
She even joked with me.

796
00:37:26,519 --> 00:37:27,559
She said, "Anton,

797
00:37:28,159 --> 00:37:29,320
look, this place isn't bad.

798
00:37:30,079 --> 00:37:31,079
There's a breeze."

799
00:37:31,199 --> 00:37:31,800
It's cool.

800
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:33,719
And it saves money.

801
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:35,840
Let's just live here from now on."

802
00:37:36,719 --> 00:37:37,320
At that moment,

803
00:37:39,599 --> 00:37:40,760
I felt terrible inside.

804
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:43,079
I swore to myself

805
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:47,559
I'd make something of myself.

806
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,400
How could I let

807
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:50,559
the person I love

808
00:37:50,559 --> 00:37:51,719
suffer like this with me?

809
00:37:55,119 --> 00:37:55,840
Later,

810
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,159
I made it.

811
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,119
Got rich.

812
00:38:00,239 --> 00:38:02,119
I bought my wife bags,

813
00:38:02,639 --> 00:38:03,559
gold jewelry,

814
00:38:04,159 --> 00:38:05,440
all the expensive things.

815
00:38:10,079 --> 00:38:11,679
But she chose to leave me.

816
00:38:13,079 --> 00:38:14,119
I didn't understand.

817
00:38:14,639 --> 00:38:15,599
I chased after her and asked,

818
00:38:15,599 --> 00:38:16,320
Why?

819
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:17,239
Why would you?

820
00:38:17,559 --> 00:38:19,400
I gave you everything good.

821
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,679
But guess what she said?

822
00:38:23,079 --> 00:38:24,840
She said, "None of this is what I want.

823
00:38:29,239 --> 00:38:30,599
I just want a home.

824
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:32,679
A home with

825
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:33,559
you

826
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:35,000
and me

827
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:38,559
is enough."

828
00:38:42,119 --> 00:38:42,760
But now,

829
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,599
I've lost everything.

830
00:39:10,519 --> 00:39:11,519
Are you free tomorrow?

831
00:39:12,159 --> 00:39:12,920
I'll come see you.

832
00:39:13,199 --> 00:39:14,159
I have something to tell you.

833
00:39:24,679 --> 00:39:25,599
Are you free tomorrow?

834
00:39:26,079 --> 00:39:27,280
Want to go hiking together?

