00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:15,880
Okay.

837
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:17,199
Okay.

838
00:40:29,079 --> 00:40:29,840
There was a time

839
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:31,719
I loved coming here to watch the sunrise

840
00:40:32,559 --> 00:40:35,159
The sun peeked out from behind Bogda Peak

841
00:40:35,639 --> 00:40:37,679
The whole city was bathed in golden light

842
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,000
Even if it lasted just a moment

843
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,840
But in that instant

844
00:40:42,079 --> 00:40:43,480
I wished time could freeze

845
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:45,360
Is it only that moment you want to freeze?

846
00:40:46,159 --> 00:40:47,000
There are others too

847
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:50,239
Life has many beautiful moments

848
00:40:51,199 --> 00:40:52,559
Once, on the grasslands

849
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,719
The moon was huge that night

850
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:55,400
So bright

851
00:40:55,639 --> 00:40:57,360
Suddenly, a red fox appeared

852
00:40:58,119 --> 00:41:01,480
When it met my gaze under the moonlight

853
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,679
It was truly beyond words

854
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:05,239
Didn't you want to take a picture?

855
00:41:05,400 --> 00:41:06,639
There was no time at all

856
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,599
Even my breathing was soft

857
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:10,199
Afraid I'd startle it

858
00:41:11,039 --> 00:41:11,639
Nana

859
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,639
I have a gift for you

860
00:41:34,079 --> 00:41:34,800
Thank you

861
00:41:36,199 --> 00:41:37,199
I really like it

862
00:41:37,519 --> 00:41:38,320
I like it too

863
00:41:39,199 --> 00:41:40,000
It's not just the painting

864
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,000
Gulinaar

865
00:41:55,599 --> 00:41:56,480
I like you

866
00:42:04,199 --> 00:42:05,039
Not the way we liked each other

867
00:42:05,039 --> 00:42:06,320
When we played together as kids

868
00:42:07,239 --> 00:42:08,280
Not the feeling after we reunited

869
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,760
Or met again

870
00:42:10,199 --> 00:42:11,320
Nor the fondness from spending time

871
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,960
And growing close

872
00:42:13,519 --> 00:42:14,719
It's a love I've thought through

873
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:18,639
You are the one I want to protect

874
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,320
And be with for my whole life

875
00:42:21,559 --> 00:42:22,760
Only then could I say I love you

876
00:42:24,599 --> 00:42:25,199
You know

877
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,360
I've come this far

878
00:42:27,519 --> 00:42:28,280
Because behind me

879
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:30,079
There's a big family loving me

880
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:30,880
Raising me

881
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:33,119
They're always standing behind me

882
00:42:33,559 --> 00:42:34,639
I have to carry them with me

883
